<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/295c7ca90724.jpg" width="818" height="394" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
</p>
<h3>
	STRATOSPHERE LAMP by Page Thirty Three
</h3>
<p>
	<span>灯光本身就有安神的作用，这盏带有<span>特别的仪式感，有种令人安心的气质。</span>灯罩使用了澳洲青石，中间的白色灯管围合在两个半圆的青石灯罩之间，可开可合，也调节了灯光的明暗。这盏灯可以平放或者立在桌面上，光线从缝隙里透出来，是发散的，给需要在睡觉时留灯的人。</span>产品来自悉尼工作室 Page Thirty Three 以“触觉等式”为主题的系列，<a href="http://www.pagethirtythree.com/tactile-equations/" target="_blank">点击这里可查看详细信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/8febd9924c09.jpg" width="812" height="493" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/8d50c2fa3ba9.jpg" width="588" height="410" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/168256b7a257.jpg" width="1080" height="718" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/d8cdd073973c.jpg" width="1080" height="480" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
